# Business persona changes must cover both platforms

When implementing any feature, fix, or update that touches the **business persona**
(business owners, business locations, business settings, business orders,
business catalog, business accounts), the change MUST be reflected on **both**:

- `apps/frontend/src/` (React web app)
- `mobile-rendasua/src/` (Expo React Native mobile app)

Do not implement a business-facing change on only one platform without explicitly
noting why the other platform is intentionally excluded.

## Examples

**Good**: Commission field is now admin-only on both web and mobile.

**Bad**: Commission field is admin-only on web but still editable on mobile.

**Acceptable with explanation**: Auto-withdraw is hidden for Stripe rail on web,
but mobile doesn't support Stripe rail yet (documented in PR).
